<template>
  <form id="Auth-View">
    <section class="d-flex flex-column main-form w-50 align-center main-form">
      <input class="form-control form-control-lg" type="text" placeholder="Username"
        aria-label=".form-control-lg example">
      <input class="form-control form-control-lg" type="text" placeholder="Password"
        aria-label=".form-control-lg example">
      <button v:on:click="AuthUser" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </section>
  </form>

  <button v:on:click="AuthUser">random button</button>
</template>


<script>

import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  name: "Auth-View",
  data() {
    return {
      dataLogin: {
        username: null,
        password: null
      }

    };
  },
  methods: {
    AuthUser() {
      axios.post("http://localhost:3000/api/user/", {
        usernam: 'Fred',
        password: 'Flintstone'
      })
        .then(function (response) {
          console.log(response);
        })
        .catch(function (error) {
          console.log(error);
        });
    }
  }
}

</script>
